            </div>
            <div class="normaltext">    
                <p>The assessment of the building is the due diligence associated with the installation of solar project. The following points is to be checked and verified before installation:</p>

    <ol>
        <li>South-facing roof</li>
        <li>Shadow free space on the roof</li>
